law.text:
Each marketing document that sets forth the health care services of a health maintenance organization shall describe fully and clearly:
The health care services under each benefit package and every other benefit to which a member is entitled;
Where and how services may be obtained;
Each exclusion or limitation on any service or other benefit that it provides;
Each deductible feature;
Each copayment provision; and
All information required by § 15-1206 of the Insurance Article.
